---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Background Glow FX -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#007cf0]/10 via-[#7928ca]/10 to-[#ff0080]/5 blur-[130px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00dfd8]/5 via-[#f9cb28]/5 to-emerald-500/5 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 relative">
    <article class="space-y-8 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-widest block">
          About Us
        </span>
        <h1 class="font-sans text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-white tracking-tight transition-colors">
          Democratizing Global Travel Access
        </h1>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">
          The Global Visa Tracker project was created with a singular mission: to make international travel requirements transparent, structured, and instantly accessible. In an era where entry rules shift dynamically due to geopolitical ties and bilateral treaties, travelers deserve a reliable reference guide to check mobility rules before planning journeys.
        </p>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-900" />

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h2 class="font-sans text-lg font-medium text-zinc-950 dark:text-white transition-colors">
          Our Technology & Real-Time Lookups
        </h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Behind our minimal and highly optimized user interface lies an structured in-memory relational lookup database matrix tracking bilateral passport rules across 197 countries and territories. We cross-reference traveler nationalities against destination territories instantly, categorizing outcomes into clean visa-free stay limits, online electronic application portal eligibility (eVisas/eTAs), border checkpoint visas (Visa on Arrival), and embassy visa mandates.
        </p>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">
          By combining this lookup engine with aggregated travel alert news feeds and direct government application portal references, we build a single point of truth for global travelers looking to secure admission policies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>

  <!-- Reusable Footer -->
  <Footer />


</Layout>
